snippet.title: Area 51 (1995) - Intro/Gameplay clip
snippet.description: Quick gameplay clip plus attract mode from Area 51. Originally released for arcades in 1995. This version is 1996 Playstation version. Game uses live action actors in some of the scenes. Game has pretty catchy music.
